A curses-based Pong clone.

Mostly to experiment with design patterns for the game engine from the Game
Programming Patterns book.

HOW TO PLAY
-----------

Player 1:
  A -- left
  S -- right

Player 2:
  K -- left
  L -- right

Q to quit.

